---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Catering in Sealy, TX - Los Cabos Mexican Grill" description="Tex-Mex catering for Sealy and surrounding areas. 500+ events catered. Free delivery inside Sealy city limits. Book online or call (512) 607-6232.">

<main class="cat-sales">

  <section class="sales-hero">
    <div class="sales-hero-overlay"></div>
    <img src="/images/cabosvan2.jpeg" alt="Los Cabos catering van at event" class="sales-hero-bg" />
    <div class="sales-hero-inner">
      <div class="sales-hero-eyebrow">CATERING · SEALY &amp; SURROUNDING AREAS</div>
      <h1 class="sales-hero-h1"><span class="sh-line">WE CATER</span><span class="sh-line">THE WHOLE</span><span class="sh-line sh-accent">FIESTA</span></h1>
      <p class="sales-hero-sub">Sizzling fajitas, stacked enchiladas, fresh pico - delivered hot, set up clean, gone in minutes. From 25 to 500+ guests.</p>
      <div class="sales-hero-ctas">
        <a href="/catering/order" class="btn-primary">Build Your Order</a>
        <a href="tel:+15126076232" class="btn-outline">Call (512) 607-6232</a>
        <a href="/catering-menu.pdf" class="btn-ghost" download="Los-Cabos-Catering-Menu.pdf">Download Menu PDF</a>
      </div>
      <div class="sales-hero-meta">
        <span>500+ events catered</span>
        <span>30-mile serving radius</span>
        <span>Minimum 25 guests</span>
        <span>Free delivery inside Sealy</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sales-why">
    <div class="sales-container">
      <div class="sales-eyebrow">WHY TEXANS CHOOSE LOS CABOS</div>
      <h2 class="sales-h2">Catering that tastes like home - at scale</h2>
      <p class="sales-lede">Feeding Sealy, Katy, Brookshire, Bellville, Columbus, Houston and all of Austin County. Scratch kitchen, honest prices, real people answering the phone.</p>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card"><h3>Fresh off the grill</h3><p>Fajitas marinated in-house and seared on open flame. Enchiladas rolled to order. Guacamole mashed the morning of.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>Delivery, setup, cleanup</h3><p>We deliver, set up on chafers with sternos, and break it all down when you are done.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>Actual humans</h3><p>Call (512) 607-6232 and you will get a real person. Changes 48 hours out? No problem.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>Plates included</h3><p>Every buffet package comes with plates, utensils and napkins. No trip to the dollar store.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sales-packages">
    <div class="sales-container">
      <div class="sales-eyebrow">BUFFET PACKAGES</div>
      <h2 class="sales-h2">Pick a package. We handle the rest.</h2>
      <p class="sales-lede">Per person pricing. Plates and plasticware included. Free delivery inside Sealy city limits.</p>
      <div class="pkg-grid">
        <a href="/catering/order" class="pkg-card pkg-popular"><div class="pkg-ribbon">MOST POPULAR</div><div class="pkg-price">$17.95<span>/person</span></div><div class="pkg-name">Famous Fajita Buffet</div><ul><li>Beef &amp; Chicken Fajitas</li><li>Cheese Enchiladas</li><li>Rice &amp; Beans</li><li>Guacamole, Pico &amp; Sour Cream</li><li>Homemade Tortillas</li><li>Chips &amp; Salsa</li></ul></a>
        <a href="/catering/order" class="pkg-card"><div class="pkg-price">$12.99<span>/person</span></div><div class="pkg-name">Taco &amp; Enchilada Buffet</div><ul><li>Cheese Enchiladas</li><li>Chicken Quesadillas</li><li>Build-Your-Own Crispy Tacos</li><li>Rice &amp; Beans</li><li>Chips &amp; Salsa</li></ul></a>
        <a href="/catering/order" class="pkg-card"><div class="pkg-price">$13.99<span>/person</span></div><div class="pkg-name">American Country</div><ul><li>Chicken Fried Steak, Chicken w/ Country Gravy, or Hamburger Steak</li><li>Plus 2 sides</li></ul></a>
        <a href="/catering/order" class="pkg-card"><div class="pkg-price">$14.99<span>/person</span></div><div class="pkg-name">Chicken &amp; Pasta</div><ul><li>Grilled Chicken Breast</li><li>Fettuccini w/ Garlic Bread</li><li>Choice of side &amp; salad</li></ul></a>
        <a href="/catering/order" class="pkg-card pkg-premium"><div class="pkg-ribbon">PREMIUM</div><div class="pkg-price">$23.99<span>/person</span></div><div class="pkg-name">Tenderloin Buffet</div><ul><li>Tenderloin Tips w/ Brown Gravy</li><li>Mashed Potatoes + 1 side</li><li>Caesar or Dinner Salad</li></ul></a>
        <a href="/catering/order" class="pkg-card"><div class="pkg-price">Custom</div><div class="pkg-name">A La Carte Only</div><ul><li>Skip the buffet, just order trays, gallons, and extras</li></ul></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="sales-tst">
    <div class="sales-container">
      <div class="sales-eyebrow">REAL REVIEWS</div>
      <h2 class="sales-h2">What our neighbors say</h2>
      <div class="tst-grid">
        <div class="tst-card"><div class="tst-stars">STAR STAR STAR STAR STAR</div><p>Catered our daughter's Quinceanera for 180 guests. Everything showed up hot and beautiful. Fajitas disappeared in twenty minutes.</p><div class="tst-who">- Maria G., Sealy</div></div>
        <div class="tst-card"><div class="tst-stars">STAR STAR STAR STAR STAR</div><p>We use Los Cabos for quarterly office lunches. Stupid-easy to order, they set up, they clean up, nobody complains.</p><div class="tst-who">- Office Manager, Katy</div></div>
        <div class="tst-card"><div class="tst-stars">STAR STAR STAR STAR STAR</div><p>Called two days before a memorial for 75 people. They made it work. Tenderloin buffet was the best comfort we could give our family.</p><div class="tst-who">- Robert H., Bellville</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sales-faq">
    <div class="sales-container">
      <div class="sales-eyebrow">COMMON QUESTIONS</div>
      <h2 class="sales-h2">Straight answers</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How far in advance do I need to book?</div><div class="faq-a">72 hours is the sweet spot. We try to make shorter notice work when we can - call us.</div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">What is the minimum head count?</div><div class="faq-a">25 guests for buffet packages. A la carte trays have no minimum.</div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Do you deliver outside Sealy?</div><div class="faq-a">Yes - up to 30 miles. Free inside Sealy city limits; modest fee beyond that.</div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Service fees or gratuity?</div><div class="faq-a">Posted prices are per-person food only. Full-service staffing available for added fee - ask when we quote you.</div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Can I mix buffet + a la carte?</div><div class="faq-a">Yes. The order builder lets you pick a buffet and add trays, gallons, and extras on top. Or go a la carte only.</div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Dietary restrictions?</div><div class="faq-a">Vegetable fajitas, cheese enchiladas, and sides cover most. Tell us about serious allergies in the notes.</div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How do I pay?</div><div class="faq-a">We confirm payment when we confirm your order - card, check, or invoice for repeat corporate clients.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sales-final">
    <div class="sales-final-inner">
      <h2 class="sales-final-h2">Let us feed your people.</h2>
      <p class="sales-final-sub">Start with our 2-minute order builder, or call us directly.</p>
      <div class="sales-final-ctas">
        <a href="/catering/order" class="btn-primary sales-cta-xl">Build Your Order</a>
        <a href="tel:+15126076232" class="btn-outline sales-cta-xl">Call (512) 607-6232</a>
      </div>
      <div class="sales-final-meta">Serving Sealy and a 30-mile radius · Free delivery inside Sealy city limits · 25 guest minimum · 500+ events catered</div>
      <a href="/catering-menu.pdf" class="sales-final-dl" download="Los-Cabos-Catering-Menu.pdf">Or download the full menu PDF</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>


<style>
  .cat-sales { background: #FBF5E9; color: #1A1410; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; }
  .sales-container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
  .sales-eyebrow { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: #E2721F; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .sales-h2 { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 56px); line-height: 1; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 16px; }
  .sales-lede { font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.55; color: #4a3f34; max-width: 720px; margin: 0 0 40px; }

  .sales-hero { position: relative; min-height: 78vh; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 140px 0 80px; color: #fff; overflow: hidden; }
  .sales-hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; z-index: 0; }
  .sales-hero-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.55), rgba(0,0,0,0.75)); z-index: 1; }
  .sales-hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; text-align: center; }
  .sales-hero-eyebrow { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.2em; font-size: 13px; color: #ffd8b5; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .sales-hero-h1 { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(56px, 11vw, 130px); line-height: 0.92; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 24px; text-transform: uppercase; text-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
  .sh-line { display: block; }
  .sh-accent { color: #F4621F; font-style: italic; }
  .sales-hero-sub { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto 36px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); }
  .sales-hero-ctas { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .sales-hero-meta { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 24px; justify-content: center; font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }

  .sales-why, .sales-packages, .sales-tst, .sales-faq { padding: 80px 0; }
  .sales-why { background: #FBF5E9; }
  .sales-packages { background: #fff; }
  .sales-tst { background: #FBF5E9; }
  .sales-faq { background: #fff; }

  .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; margin-top: 40px; }
  .why-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(226,114,31,0.18); border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px 24px; }
  .why-card h3 { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 22px; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 8px; }
  .why-card p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55; color: #4a3f34; margin: 0; }

  .pkg-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 40px; }
  .pkg-card { position: relative; display: block; background: #fff; border: 2px solid rgba(226,114,31,0.25); border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px 24px; text-decoration: none; color: #1A1410; transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s; overflow: hidden; }
  .pkg-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: #E2721F; }
  .pkg-popular { border-color: #E2721F; }
  .pkg-premium { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff, #fef5e8); border-color: #c08c30; }
  .pkg-ribbon { position: absolute; top: 14px; right: -34px; transform: rotate(35deg); background: #E2721F; color: #fff; font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.14em; font-size: 12px; padding: 4px 40px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .pkg-price { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 40px; color: #E2721F; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .pkg-price span { font-size: 15px; color: #7a6d5f; font-weight: 600; }
  .pkg-name { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 22px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .pkg-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; font-size: 14.5px; color: #4a3f34; }
  .pkg-card li { padding: 5px 0; }

  .tst-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; margin-top: 40px; }
  .tst-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px 24px; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
  .tst-stars { color: #f5c518; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 800; }
  .tst-card p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.55; color: #2b2520; margin: 0 0 14px; font-style: italic; }
  .tst-who { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; font-size: 13px; color: #C25610; text-transform: uppercase; }

  .faq-list { max-width: 820px; margin: 40px auto 0; }
  .faq-item { background: #FBF5E9; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 18px 22px; border-left: 3px solid #E2721F; }
  .faq-q { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .faq-a { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55; color: #4a3f34; }

  .sales-final { padding: 100px 24px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A1410, #3a2817); color: #fff; text-align: center; }
  .sales-final-inner { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .sales-final-h2 { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 64px); line-height: 1; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 16px; }
  .sales-final-sub { font-size: 18px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin: 0 0 32px; }
  .sales-final-ctas { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .sales-cta-xl { padding: 20px 42px !important; font-size: 17px !important; }
  .sales-final-meta { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .sales-final-dl { color: #ffd8b5; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: underline; }

  @media (max-width: 639px) {
    .sales-hero { min-height: 0; padding: 100px 0 60px; }
    .sales-hero-ctas { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
    .sales-hero-ctas a { width: 100%; }
    .sales-hero-meta { gap: 8px 16px; font-size: 12px; }
    .sales-final-ctas { flex-direction: column; }
    .sales-final-ctas a { width: 100%; }
    .sales-why, .sales-packages, .sales-tst, .sales-faq { padding: 56px 0; }
  }
</style>

</Layout>
